---
title: Greek-Inspired Chicken Breasts Salad with Olives and Feta
description: Is there anything better than a classic creamy Greek dressing?! Tonight, juicy Mediterranean-spiced chicken sits atop a Greek-inspired salad with peppers and tomatoes. Briny olives and feta cheese create a perfect salty finish!
